          "INC-SPECT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                " EN-RSL-HW - the total beam spread in the foil, which",
                "consists of energy loss convoluted with the straggling."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "A stack of yttrium foils, interspersed with aluminum",
                "foils, is irradiated with an accurately measured beam",
                "of particles.",
                " Targets were of a purity 99.5 and 99.9% and were",
                "obtained from two independent vendors.",
                "Densities varied from 5 to 11 mg/cm2 and the foils",
                "were 25.4 mm in diameter.",
                "1.275-g/cm aluminum absorbers were used."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "GELI"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                ""
              ]
            }
          ],
