              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "ERR-1",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The statistical and systematic errors. To these",
                "numbers, ERR-2 and ERR-3 should be added in quadrature."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "ERR-2",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The error due to foil uniformity"
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "ERR-3",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The error due to counter calibration",
                " Decay-scheme errors are insignificant in comparison."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ADD-RES": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "COMP"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The cross sections are also calculated with",
                "phenomenological preequilibrium models (exciton,",
